data.description: Welcome Home! You will fall for this split entry 4 bedroom / 3 bathroom charmer with beamed ceiling and large backyard. Big windows make this home warm & bright. Special features include hardwood bedrooms, tiled floors, open kitchen & floor plan. Two large siding doors leading to the large deck overlooking a beautiful fenced yard. The layout of the home creates more room than expected with updated space in the lower level.
